A time-traveling bunny adventure video game where players take on the role of a bunny named Benny who has stumbled upon a mysterious time-traveling device. Benny must navigate through different time periods, from ancient Egypt to the Wild West, to fix temporal anomalies and prevent a catastrophic future.

A children's book series featuring a time-traveling bunny named Binky who travels through history with his trusty sidekick, a wise old owl named Hootie. Each book takes the duo to a different historical era, where they encounter famous figures and events, and learn about the culture and customs of each time period.

A live-action/CGI movie about a bunny named Max who discovers a magical time-traveling carrot that allows him to visit different eras and meet famous historical figures. Max must use his wit and resourcefulness to fix a broken timeline and save the world from destruction.

A time-traveling bunny podcast where a group of friends explore different historical events and figures through the eyes of a bunny. Each episode takes the group to a different time period, where they interview historical figures and witness key events firsthand.

A time-traveling bunny board game where players take on the role of a bunny named Rosie who must navigate through different time periods to collect historical artifacts and fix temporal anomalies. The game includes different challenge cards that require players to solve puzzles and complete tasks to progress through the game.
